584
00:48:40,542 --> 00:48:42,542
Zarazte je!

585
00:48:43,709 --> 00:48:45,333
Musíte tedy bojovat.

586
00:48:45,542 --> 00:48:49,625
Ta doba nastala, mnoho
času jste strávili

587
00:48:49,959 --> 00:48:52,291
